{"tid":1191834,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公屋叫價777萬 代理:「補地價近50%」","createTime":"2019-06-08T06:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T03:32:56.000Z","uid":42188,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"86727cf743df3d31bb92563b4d5de0b648208038","tid":1191834,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"現時二手樓放盤買少見少，有樓在手的業主都有個天價賣樓夢，於是吊高來賣。去年12月，屯門公屋建生邨驚見有單位叫價800萬元，成市場熱話。雖然單位之後已減價至750萬元，但放盤至今兩個月，仍然待售中。<br />\n<br />\n繼建生邨後，同區另一公屋良景邨亦出現癲價放盤。祥益地產黃慶德表示，良景邨良賢樓中層12室，實用面積531方呎，業主2002年向房屋署以16.43萬元買入單位自住，過年前放盤，居屋第二市場（未補價地價）叫價380萬元，呎價7,156元，自由市場同時放盤，因公屋補地價折扣率相當高，要近50%，業主又希望淨袋380萬元，所以計及補價因素，開價竟達777萬元，呎價14,633元，比建生邨叫價更癲，挑戰做全港最貴公屋。<br />\n<br />\n目前全港最貴公屋為沙田顯徑邨，成交價530萬元，是次良景邨放盤較之貴接近一半。而目前全港呎價最貴公屋則為青衣長安邨，呎價逾1.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n位於屯門田景路31號的良景邨，1988年入伙，由8幢大廈組成，單位數目2,400伙。房委會資料顯示，截至去年底，良景邨單位租住數目為2,300伙。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知而家賣咗未呢？定Strong Hold緊？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf799664a79fee9411598eeb192121f49232a50","tid":1191834,"uid":72058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541909fb38251b26be318f9c0d95918d8ac1b9ed","tid":1191834,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"佢係咪比aa煩所以鳩開價"},{"pid":"cba6cfa96d37c76862ca3fa5aa88817e57b1e4b7","tid":1191834,"uid":19552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ccf799664a79fee9411598eeb192121f49232a50","tid":1191834,"uid":72058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"記得果陣有好熟樓市既連登仔話d人唔知米價亂屌 呢個價好正常<br />\n<br />\n屌那星 原來貴過瓏門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422156a3ef41f63f74bbcf4dfd5f45bd544ec53d","tid":1191834,"uid":122377,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:52:52.000Z","msg":"真係好撚到弱智業主 <br />\n以後賣樓應該要先驗智商 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc9b6e248fbe67ea074efaf775c6666d95d43b5","tid":1191834,"uid":163783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"公屋邊有人會買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撞著隔離果個癡線既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0077b58645dc9dd240c851e8a606e31fa5877bb4","tid":1191834,"uid":151955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fc9b6e248fbe67ea074efaf775c6666d95d43b5","tid":1191834,"uid":163783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"公屋邊有人會買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撞著隔離果個癡線既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"如果得三條路<br />\n1. 每月$5000租150尺劏房<br />\n2. 每月$5000供間300尺公屋<br />\n3. 自殺<br />\n你會點揀？"},{"pid":"dc3fc10841d89eadce22576f9d969603a4ab10c4","tid":1191834,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"下次搵個放盤賣一個億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a83b50df4bf35f6bb7489040023cf0347116387","tid":1191834,"uid":73092,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0077b58645dc9dd240c851e8a606e31fa5877bb4","tid":1191834,"uid":151955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fc9b6e248fbe67ea074efaf775c6666d95d43b5","tid":1191834,"uid":163783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"公屋邊有人會買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj